data.description: Discover the allure of this charming 2-bed, 1-bath brick cape is a beacon of comfort and convenience, just steps away from uptown Kingston. Hardwood floors adorn the first floor, where two cozy bedrooms and a full bath await. The kitchen-dining combo is complemented by a delightful screened porch, perfect for those warm summer nights. Upstairs, a versatile bonus room opens doors to endless possibilities. Step into the backyard oasis, complete with a lovely paver patio   an ideal spot to create memories with family and friends. Embrace the walkable lifestyle with proximity to schools, Forsyth Park, the zoo, bus station, and a plethora of restaurants and shops. This is not just a home; it's an invitation to a vibrant community. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!
